: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWriting: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\tBlow dryer<br />\n\tA blow dryer is an appliance commonly used for drying hair. What does the blow dryer look like? Who is using it? What will be the outcome?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: A blow dryer was used... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) a hair stylist using a blow dryer<br />\n\t2) a blow dryer with a new design</p>\n<p>\n\t3) unplugging a blow dryer<br />\n\t4) using a blow dryer in a hotel room<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tHe never liked the noise the blow dryer made, as he found it loud and annoying. He always preferred to have his hair dry naturally if time allowed. For Sean, if his hair was towel dried enough, it took little to no time to dry naturally. When taking a shower in the morning before work, he would want to blow dry his hair and be completely presentable and professional the moment he stepped out of the change room. As for now, time is more pressing. That was why Sean decided to let his hair dry naturally.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/1710182572438/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p912804/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p912804\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p973071/\">2016年12月英语六级真题答案发布【试卷一】（文都教育版）</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p97